00:41:39.230 --> 00:41:42.090
Pengarah Mao memberinya tiket
ke China Taiwan.

00:41:45.110 --> 00:41:46.650
Tetapi dia menolaknya.

00:41:46.670 --> 00:41:50.650
Katanya nak berkhidmat di Shanghai.

00:41:55.590 --> 00:41:56.090
Jadi?

